<plot>The film follows Story Hero as he goes out attempting to flirt with girls instructed by a voiceover. Shot as a black and white silent comedy, TAoF is an instructional guide showing us how to flirt. TAoF is contemporary but uses the silent movie style to emphasise flirting as primarily non-verbal and to demonstrate flirting is a classic and somewhat neglected art. TAoF is also a homage to the silent comedies of Buster Keaton.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?540837</url></doc>
